                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Slight chance of a shower in the west, near zero chance elsewhere. Winds westerly 15 to 20 km/h tending southwesterly 20 to 30 km/h in the morning then becoming light in the late evening. Daytime maximum temperatures around 19.</text>
